{"fadeType":2,"once":true,"scripts":[{"mode":1,"stopbgm":true,"sequence":[["The Miniature Head Maid\n\n<size=45>Chapter 2 - Accidents Have Consequences<\/size>",1]]},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"say":"Port - A Few Days Ago","dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_task","bgm":"story-1"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Ready, nya?","dir":1,"actorName":"{namecode:98}","side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"bgName":"bg_story_task","actor":312010},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","paintingFadeOut":{"side":0,"time":0.5},"say":"Yep. Just give the word.","dir":1,"actorName":"{namecode:37}","side":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"bgName":"bg_story_task","actor":302010},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Hit it, nya! Commence \"Wisdom Cube Composition Analysis Test #256,\" nya!","dir":1,"actorName":"{namecode:98}","side":0,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"bgName":"bg_story_task","actor":312010},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"It's fair to say the Wisdom Cubes are sort of like our keels.","dir":1,"actorName":"{namecode:37}","side":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"bgName":"bg_story_task","actor":302010},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"If there's something wrong with your keel, you're in big trouble, nya.","dir":1,"actorName":"{namecode:98}","side":0,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"bgName":"bg_story_task","actor":312010},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Although it's common knowledge we were born from the Wisdom Cubes, no one has ever successfully analyzed the internal composition of the cubes themselves...","dir":1,"actorName":"{namecode:37}","side":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"bgName":"bg_story_task","actor":302010},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"The only way to get our hands on a Wisdom Cube is to harvest 'em, nya... They're what you'd call a \"black box,\" nya...","dir":1,"actorName":"{namecode:98}","side":0,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"bgName":"bg_story_task","actor":312010},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"But this time is different! This time we have this!","dir":1,"actorName":"{namecode:37}","side":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"bgName":"bg_story_task","actor":302010},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"This \"weapon\" we got from a battle with the Sirens, nya.","dir":1,"actorName":"{namecode:98}","side":0,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"bgName":"bg_story_task","actor":312010},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"We've tentatively named it the \"Focused Beam Emitter.\"","dir":1,"actorName":"{namecode:37}","side":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"bgName":"bg_story_task","actor":302010},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"While we don't yet understand the principles at work, we do know that the device emits a heat ray with tremendous penetrative power when stimulated by a high voltage direct current, nya.","dir":1,"actorName":"{namecode:98}","side":0,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"bgName":"bg_story_task","actor":312010},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"We had a little problem last time... Yuubari said we oughta try recharging it, nya. Result was a base-wide blackout, and damn near a hole in my head, nya...","dir":1,"actorName":"{namecode:98}","side":0,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"bgName":"bg_story_task","actor":312010},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"We must be willing to make sacrifices in the name of science...","dir":1,"actorName":"{namecode:37}","side":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"bgName":"bg_story_task","actor":302010},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Safety comes first, nya...","dir":1,"actorName":"{namecode:98}","side":0,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"bgName":"bg_story_task","actor":312010},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"We've prepared a large capacitor to guard against any power surges this time.","dir":1,"actorName":"{namecode:37}","side":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"bgName":"bg_story_task","actor":302010},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"So I don't expect we'll run into any such problems again...","dir":1,"actorName":"{namecode:37}","side":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"bgName":"bg_story_task","actor":302010},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Let's run through the experiment one more time, nya!","dir":1,"actorName":"{namecode:98}","side":0,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"bgName":"bg_story_task","actor":312010},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"We will direct the high-energy heat ray at the Wisdom Cube in an attempt to disintegrate or penetrate it, that we may analyze its internal composition.","dir":1,"actorName":"{namecode:37}","side":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"bgName":"bg_story_task","actor":302010},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Wisdom Cube and Emitter in position nya! We're gonna see some serious shit, nya...","dir":1,"actorName":"{namecode:98}","side":0,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"bgName":"bg_story_task","actor":312010},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Engaging. Countdown: three, two...","dir":1,"actorName":"{namecode:37}","side":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"bgName":"bg_story_task","actor":302010},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"Madam Akashi, I've come to retrieve those docu—","actor":202120,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_task","na